```mermaid
flowchart TD
  CREATE[Flag Created\nexpiresAt set\nowner assigned] --> DARK[Dark Launch\n0% exposure]
  DARK --> CANARY[Canary\n1-5% exposure]
  CANARY --> CHECK1{Health gates\npassing?}
  CHECK1 -->|Yes| RAMP[Gradual Ramp\n10% → 50% → 100%]
  CHECK1 -->|No| ROLLBACK1[Rollback to 0%\nInvestigate]
  RAMP --> CHECK2{All metrics\nnormal?}
  CHECK2 -->|Yes| FULL[Full Release\n100%]
  CHECK2 -->|No| ROLLBACK2[Reduce exposure\nInvestigate]
  FULL --> CLEANUP[Schedule Cleanup\nbefore expiresAt]
  CLEANUP --> REMOVE[Remove flag from code\nArchive flag definition]

  subgraph KillSwitch [Kill Switch Path]
    ALERT[Alert fires\nincident declared] --> DISABLE[On-call disables flag\nvia Management API]
    DISABLE --> SSE_PUSH[SSE pushed to all instances\n< 5s SLO]
    SSE_PUSH --> REVERT[Feature disabled\nfor all users]
    REVERT --> POSTMORTEM[Post-mortem\nfix root cause]
    POSTMORTEM --> REENABLE[Re-enable when safe\nor remove flag permanently]
  end
```
